    .container 
        .solutions__wrapper 
            .solutions__heading(data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-delay="400")
                p Meet 
                img(src="../images/quipli_logo_yellow.svg", alt="quipli logo yellow")
            p.solutions__title(data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-delay="300") Get your life back with the only rental software you’ll ever need
            p.solutions__descr(data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-delay="200") In one clean solution, we tie it all together so you can focus on running and growing your business. From an ecommerce storefront to inventory management, Quipli is your new one-stop shop for rental software.
